    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and remains a dependable daily driver. The engine and transmission are functional, though you may notice some minor cosmetic wear on the exterior and the interior upholstery shows its age. It has been regularly serviced, but a buyer should expect some upcoming maintenance items typical for its mileage. Overall, it\u2019s a solid, honest car for someone looking for reliable transportation at a reasonable price point.",
