    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "For sale is a functional vehicle in fair condition, suitable for someone looking for an affordable transportation option. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some paint fading on the roof, and a few small dings on the passenger side doors. Inside, the upholstery has some visible staining and the driver's seat shows significant wear, though all major electronics and the air conditioning still work. Mechanically, it runs and drives, but it does have a slow oil leak and the suspension is starting to feel loose over bumps. It's a solid project car or a basic point-A-to-point-B commuter that will likely need some mechanical attention in the near future.",
      "price": 22500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional acquisition for the refined collector: a vehicle in truly immaculate condition. This specimen has been preserved to an exacting standard, exhibiting a flawless exterior profile and an interior that retains its original factory integrity. Meticulously maintained and mechanically beyond reproach, this motorcar offers an uncompromising driving experience that mirrors its showroom-debut state. An investment-grade example for those who demand nothing less than automotive excellence.",
